                        <p>
                            Unprecedented interoperability
                            and
                            scalability for blockchain
                            developers who want to quickly
                            push
                            the limits of what’s possible.
                            Built
                            using Substrate with nearly the
                            same
                            codebase and industry-leading
                            multichain infrastructure as
                            Kusama’s cousin, Polkadot.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="box-graphic">
                <img
                    src="/assets/img/boxes_graph.png"
                    alt="Kusama Network"
                />
