            <section class="genesis">
                <div class="wrap">
                    <div class="wrap-left">
                        <h2>Genesis of Kusama</h2>
                        <p>The interaction between society
                            and
                            technology has evolved into a
                            broken
                            model, where large entities
                            routinely stretch and overstep
                            their
                            authority.
                            <br /><br />
                            Entrusting our information to
                            these
                            organizations presents a
                            critical
                            risk to individuals and society.
                            Kusama was built to spark
                            innovation
                            and disrupt the status quo by
                            putting next-generation tools in
                            the
                            hands of change agents.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="what-is-kusama">
                <div class="wrap">
                    <div class="wrap-right box-outlines">
                        <h2>What is Kusama?</h2>
                        <p>Kusama is a scalable network of
                            multiple specialized blockchains
                            built using the same tools and
                            nearly the same codebase as
                            Polkadot.
                            <br /><br />
                            The network is a development
                            environment for teams who want
                            to
                            move fast and innovate
                            exclusively
                            on Kusama, or prepare for
                            deployment
                            on Polkadot.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="launch-your-blockchain">
                <div class="sticky-hero">
                    <div class="bg-img">
                        <img
                            src="/assets/img/mesh_graph_1.png"
